article.headline: Stephen F.Austin 68, Texas St. 52
article.story: NACOGDOCHES, Texas -- Matt Kingsley scored 23 points to help lead Stephen F. Austin to a 68-52 victory over Texas State on Wednesday night. Kingsley hit 10-of-15 from the field and 3-of-4 free throws. Josh Alexander scored 15 points and Nick Shaw had a double-double with 11 points and 10 rebounds for Stephen F. Austin (18-7, 10-3 Southland). Brandon Bush led Texas State (12-14, 5-8) with 22 points. Stephen F. Austin led 40-21 at the half after shooting 58 percent from the field to 37 percent for Texas State.
